# No build-time secrets are required in v1.
#
# R2 credentials live ONLY in your rclone remote
# (~/.config/rclone/rclone.conf) — never in this repo. `photosite setup` writes
# them there for you.
#
# This file is a placeholder documenting where a FUTURE build-time secret would
# go. If one is ever needed, copy this to `.env` (gitignored) and set the value:
#
# EXAMPLE_FUTURE_SECRET=changeme
